# Browsers that we support

# Production browsers
> 1%
last 2 versions
Firefox ESR
not dead
not ie 11
not op_mini all

# Modern browsers for development
last 1 chrome version
last 1 firefox version
last 1 safari version
last 1 edge version

# Mobile browsers
ios_saf >= 12
android >= 6
samsung >= 10

# Specific browser versions for better compatibility
chrome >= 58
firefox >= 57
safari >= 11
edge >= 16

# Exclude problematic browsers
not ie <= 10
not op_mini all
not kaios <= 2.5